COPY AND PASTE，所以可以好快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbd59447fa4b9fa36425d75a7c002e854ade9191","tid":799364,"uid":204533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"58259251db7a2e250d23f3a6859306d3fd523f26","tid":799364,"uid":39921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cde35c2151a69c9121a626fafc2118705ea4a377","tid":799364,"uid":204533,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"dff0e9f413f02f9c39862d526d7776def6cebf9e","tid":799364,"uid":60648,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T05:32:38.000Z","msg":"古代佛教真係亡國成因<br />\n成班人入去避稅役<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T06:20:59.000Z","msg":"所以古代有人講過, 佛教入國破國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T09:34:55.000Z","msg":"點睇泰緬錫蘭柬埔寨斯里蘭卡"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T11:12:49.000Z","msg":"唔識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我回佢係討論緊, 古代有避稅避役, 令到某啲朝代經濟有嚴重問題, 所以有古人批評入國破國<br />\n但我唔熟你講個堆國家政經CONTEXT, 亦唔知有無同我篇文提及既類似既各種優惠政策, 不如你介紹下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"059d03590add215babcdb094e49ecb2736e12268","tid":799364,"uid":26329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T12:08:35.000Z","msg":"文革時期漢傳佛教正式入滅"},{"pid":"8dd23cb4f9017cb355134fcf8a4786abf9956a33","tid":799364,"uid":686,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T12:11:56.000Z","msg":"諗起以前睇三言二拍, 唔記得邊部有講一篇故仔<br />\n係講啲良家婦女入寺過夜向佛求子<br />\n半夜啲和尚輪流用地道入去間房強姦<br />\n啲女人唔敢爆出去, 驚要浸豬籠<br />\n由於俾好多人強姦, 所以通常好快懷孕<br />\n變咗越來越多人來求子 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有啲淫娃俾人姦過後仲特登去多次 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c0992191e6f25670890d8fd1373fc678f847857","tid":799364,"uid":191926,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T12:22:31.000Z","msg":"好文<br />\n根本宗教就是<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n中國佛教更係垃圾中的超級垃圾<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d2c2687527c4aa5c58f43b5121b53ddfffc8240","tid":799364,"uid":75655,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"6bde31226eb6d6bbebb8dc8f78eb0bb8263b4b13","tid":799364,"uid":26449,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T04:31:46.000Z","msg":"中國將貪、嗔、痴完美表現出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T12:28:59.000Z","msg":"其實跟返釋迦牟尼佛 原始果個概念係好, 好似原始佛念都無話人唔可以食肉, 不過依家啲仆街扭曲哂 用佛教名義 揾錢 仆野 叫雞"},{"pid":"c8be71f0d9cae389f29c7dd60aa8c474d6664f3d","tid":799364,"uid":204533,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"059d03590add215babcdb094e49ecb2736e12268","tid":799364,"uid":26329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T12:08:35.000Z","msg":"文革時期漢傳佛教正式入滅"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T12:43:41.000Z","msg":"以佛教教團黎講, 佢地繼承佢地老祖宗好多野架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://static.ettoday.net/images/2636/d2636512.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fstatic.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2636%2Fd2636512.jpg&h=3444d51a&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}